                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18170702-70-defend579 t18170702-70-punish399"></join>
               DEATH
            </rs>. Aged 16.</p>
               <p>Second Middlesex Jury, before Mr. Justice Park.</p>
